1.1
log
@Initial revision
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: key.c,v 1.10 2002/02/16 21:27:08 millert Exp $	*/
/*	$NetBSD: key.c,v 1.11 1995/09/07 06:57:11 jtc Exp $	*/

